content:
Permission set licenses extend the functionality of user licenses. With permission set licenses, you can assign more permissions to users than what their user license supports.

You can migrate your users from Managed Package Licenses (MPLs) to permission set licenses. Also, learn how to map products or licenses (SKUs) to permission set licenses and their respective permission sets.

To use group benefits in the Salesforce data model, check your add-on licenses and permission set license assignments.
